- **Locale-aware responses** – prepare error messages and user-facing strings for i18n.
- **Accept-Language header** – respect client language preferences when available.
- **Date/time formatting** – always use ISO 8601 for API responses, format for display separately.
- **Currency and number formatting** – prepare for different locale-specific formatting needs.
- **Text direction support** – consider RTL languages in data structure design.
- **Unicode support** – ensure proper UTF-8 handling for task titles and descriptions.
- **Timezone awareness** – store UTC timestamps, convert to user timezone on client-side.
